ww_testtube
	Made by Niko (TGP_Niko)

The first of many Water Wall (WW_) maps.
Play with up to 16 people.


//Install\\

place materials folder and maps folder into your cstrike folder:

C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\[YOUR STEAM NAME]\counter-strike source\cstrike

//Server install\\

place materials folder and maps folder into your server cstrike folder:

C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\[YOUR STEAM NAME]\source dedicated server\cstrike



-----------------------------------------------------------
Good Luck and have fun

-Niko
